sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Engine as CRON / Inngest Worker
    participant DB as PostgreSQL Database
    participant Service as Gateway Router Service
    participant Aggregator as Payment Gateway (M-Pesa / PayPal / Bank Rail)

    Engine->>DB: Query Subscriptions where nextBillingDate <= NOW() AND status == ACTIVE
    DB-->>Engine: Return batch of records with PaymentMethod Tokens
    
    loop Per Overdue Subscription
        Engine->>DB: Open Prisma Transaction, check/lock Ledger State
        Engine->>Service: Dispatch collection request with Token & Idempotency Key
        
        alt Gateway: PayPal / M-Pesa Standing Order / Bank Tokenized Debit
            Service->>Aggregator: Direct API Pull Request (Non-interactive)
            Aggregator-->>Service: API Response (Success / Dispatched)
        else Gateway: M-Pesa STK Fallback (Requires interaction)
            Service->>Aggregator: Push STK Push Request to handset
            Aggregator-->>Service: Acknowledged (Awaiting Callback)
        end

        Service-->>Engine: Update status to PENDING or processing token
        Engine->>DB: Commit tracking update, adjust locks
    end
